<h1 id="--max-2-faces-may-share-a-vertex-if-they-are-not-connected-through-edges-originating-from-that-vertex-required-for-the-implementation-to-differntiate-the-order-of-edges-around-an-origin">- max. 2 faces may share a vertex, if they are not connected through edges originating from that vertex; required for the implementation, to differntiate the order of edges around an origin</h1>
